## Tableaux Proving

```elixir
import ShotDs.Parser
import ShotMain.Prover
```

```elixir
"?[X: $o]: X" |> parse |> prove
```

```elixir
"a & b => a" |> parse |> prove
```

```elixir
"a => (a | b)" |> parse |> prove
```

```elixir
"~?[F : $i>$i>$o]: ![Y: $i>$o]: ?[X: $i]: F @ X = Y" |> parse |> prove
```

```elixir
"p @ (a & b) => p @ (b & a)" |> parse |> prove
```

```elixir
"![X : $o, Y : $o]: p @ X & p @ Y => p @ (X & Y)" |> parse |> prove
```

```elixir
"
(
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: X) &
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: ~X) &
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: $false) &
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: $true)
)
=>
![Y : $o>$o]: p @ Y
"
|> parse |> prove
```

```elixir
"
(
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: X) &
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: ~X) &
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: $false) &
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: $true)
)
=>
?[Y : $o>$o]: ~ p @ Y
"
|> parse |> prove
```

```elixir
"p @ a & p @ b => p @ (a & b)" |> parse |> prove
```

